<html>

<head>
	<title>Reservation Confirmation</title>
	<style type="text/css">
	div.reservationCard {
		background-color: #eeeeaa;
		color: #000000;
		padding: 1em;
		margin-bottom: 1em;
	}
	
	div.reservationCard h2 {
		font-family: Palatino, serif;
		font-style: italic;
		text-align: center;
		margin-top: 0px;
		font-size: 200%;
		font-weight: bold;
	}

	div.reservationContainer {
		width: 50%;
		margin-left: auto;
		margin-right: auto;
	}

	div.reservationContainer input {
		width: 100%;
		height: 3em;
		color: white;
		font-weight: bold;
		margin-bottom: 1em;
		font-size: 1em;
		font-weight: bold;
		border: 3px outset black;
		cursor: pointer;
	}
	</style>
</head>

<body>
	<p>Hi there <%= @user.name %>,</p>

<p>Sad news: the session on "<%= @session.topic.name %>" for which you
	had signed up has been cancelled.</p>

<% if @custom_message.present? %>
  <p><%= @custom_message %></p>
<%end%>
	
<p>If you'd like to sign up to take the class at a different time, you can
	see a list of times it is offered <%= link_to "here", :action => "show", :controller => "topics", :id => @session.topic.id, :only_path => false %>.</p>

<div class="reservationContainer">
	<div class="reservationCard">
		<h2>The Cancelled Reservation:</h2>
		<dl>
			<dt>What:</dt>
			<dd><%=h @session.topic.name %></dd>
      <dt>When:</dt>
      <% if @session.multiple_occurrences? %>
        <dd>This session meets <%= @session.occurrences.count %> times:</dd>
      <% end %>
      <% @session.occurrences.each do |o| %>
        <dd><%=h formatted_time_range(o.time, @session.topic.minutes) %></dd>
      <% end %>
			<dt>Who:</dt>
			<dd><%=h @user.name %></dd>
		</dl>
	</div>
</div>

<p>Our sincere apologies for the inconvenience.</p>
</body>

</html>

